cies\n64: \n65: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n66: |---------|---------|---------|\n67: | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] | [TO BE FILLED] |\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## Implementation Notes\n72: \n73: [TO BE FILLED: Implementation notes and constants]\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## References\n78: \n79: - cli-toolkit/design.md тАФ CLI toolkit architecture\n80: - cli-toolkit/spec.md тАФ CLI specification\n\n(End of file - total 80 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-025 тАФ MetadataService ф╕ОцХ░цНоцибхЮЛ Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-025 тАФ MetadataService ф╕ОцХ░цНоцибхЮЛ |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Describe the MetadataService and data models design overview]\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n[TO BE FILLED: System context diagram]\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","time":{"start":1775876891101,"end":1775876891110}}}}
