{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775876981361,"sessionID":"ses_2857d9e48ffeiSUh9xRkEvxJO6","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8442010014TMjdGt557CUYq","messageID":"msg_d7a82fbbc001oQBIIX77kiTBdy","sessionID":"ses_2857d9e48ffeiSUh9xRkEvxJO6","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-8f2062e67ff342a0921226379d4722c0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","content":"# AR-025 тАФ MetadataService ф╕ОцХ░цНоцибхЮЛ Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-025 тАФ MetadataService ф╕ОцХ░цНоцибхЮЛ |\n| Module | `cmd/cli` |\n| Language | Python |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\nThis AR implements the `MetadataService` and associated data models (`AgentMetadata` and `MetadataOptions`) that manage agent configuration throughout the CLI lifecycle. The service handles loading, saving, and validating YAML metadata files that persist agent state across `pack`, `build`, `publish`, `invoke`, and `status` operations.\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ                         CLI Commands                                 тФВ\nтФВ  pack тФВ build тФВ publish тФВ invoke тФВ status                           тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФмтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n                      тФВ\n                      тЦ╝\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ                      Runtime Classes                                 тФВ\nтФВ  PackRuntime тФВ BuildRuntime тФВ PublishRuntime тФВ InvokeRuntime тФВ      тФВ\nтФВ  StatusRuntime                                                       тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФмтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n                      тФВ\n                      тЦ╝\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ                      MetadataService                                 тФВ\nтФВ  - load_metadata(workspace_path) тЖТ AgentMetadata                    тФВ\nтФВ  - save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata) тЖТ None                   тФВ\nтФВ  - update_metadata(workspace_path, updates) тЖТ AgentMetadata         тФВ\nтФВ  - validate_workspace(workspace_path) тЖТ bool                        тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФмтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n                      тФВ\n                      тЦ╝\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ                      Data Models                                     тФВ\nтФВ  AgentMetadata (Pydantic BaseModel) тЖР YAML serialization            тФВ\nтФВ  MetadataOptions (dataclass) тЖР CLI options mapping                  тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n                      тФВ\n                      тЦ╝\nтФМтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФР\nтФВ                      Storage                                         тФВ\nтФВ  {workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml (canonical)                        тФВ\nтФВ  {workspace}/agent.yaml (fallback)                                  тФВ\nтФВ  {workspace}/metadata.yaml (fallback)                               тФВ\nтФФтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФАтФШ\n```\n\n---\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### AgentMetadata (Pydantic BaseModel)\n\nPrimary data model for agent configuration, stored as YAML.\n\n| Field | Type | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `agent_name` | `str` | **required** | Unique name identifying the agent |\n| `description` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Human-readable summary |\n| `language` | `str` | `\"python\"` | Programming language used |\n| `entrypoint` | `str` | **required** | Command to launch the agent |\n| `port` | `int` | `8080` | Port exposed by the agent runtime |\n| `build_mode` | `str` | `\"local\"` | Build strategy: local or cloud |\n| `region` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Deployment region |\n| `version` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Semantic version string for publishing |\n| `image` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Container image information |\n| `auth` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Authentication configuration |\n| `requirements_file` | `Optional[str]` | `\"requirements.txt\"` | Python dependency file |\n| `registry_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry URL for image publishing |\n| `registry_username` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry username |\n| `registry_password` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` | Registry password |\n| `agent_endpoint` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent endpoint URL |\n| `workload_manager_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | URL for the Workload Manager |\n| `router_url` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | URL for the Router |\n| `readiness_probe_path` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Path for the readiness probe |\n| `readiness_probe_port` | `Optional[int]` | `None` | Port for the readiness probe |\n| `agent_id` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | Agent ID assigned by AgentCube |\n| `session_id` | `Optional[str]` | `None` | The session ID for the agent |\n| `k8s_deployment` | `Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` | `None` | Kubernetes deployment information |\n\n#### Validators\n\n```python\n@field_validator('language')\n@classmethod\ndef validate_language(cls, v: str) -> str:\n    v = v.lower()\n    if v not in ['python', 'java']:\n        raise ValueError(f'language must be one of: python, java')\n    return v\n\n@field_validator('build_mode')\n@classmethod\ndef validate_build_mode(cls, v: str) -> str:\n    v = v.lower()\n    if v not in ['local', 'cloud']:\n        raise ValueError(f'build_mode must be one of: local, cloud')\n    return v\n\n@field_validator('port')\n@classmethod\ndef validate_port(cls, v: int) -> int:\n    if not (1 <= v <= 65535):\n        raise ValueError('port must be between 1 and 65535')\n    return v\n```\n\n---\n\n### MetadataOptions (dataclass)\n\nCLI options dataclass for mapping command-line arguments to metadata fields.\n\n| Field | Type | Default |\n|-------|------|---------|\n| `agent_name` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n| `language` | `Optional[str]` | `'python'` |\n| `entrypoint` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n| `port` | `Optional[int]` | `8080` |\n| `build_mode` | `Optional[str]` | `'local'` |\n| `requirements_file` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n| `description` | `Optional[str]` | `None` |\n| `workload_manager_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `router_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `readiness_probe_path` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `readiness_probe_port` | `Optional[int]` | `8080` |\n| `registry_url` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `registry_username` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `registry_password` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n| `agent_endpoint` | `Optional[str]` | `\"\"` |\n\n```python\n@dataclass\nclass MetadataOptions:\n    agent_name: Optional[str] = None\n    language: Optional[str] = 'python'\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = None\n    port: Optional[int] = 8080\n    build_mode: Optional[str] = 'local'\n    requirements_file: Optional[str] = None\n    description: Optional[str] = None\n    workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    router_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = 8080\n    registry_url: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    registry_username: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    registry_password: Optional[str] = \"\"\n    agent_endpoint: Optional[str] = \"\"\n\n    @classmethod\n    def from_options(cls, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> \"MetadataOptions\":\n        return cls(**{k: v for k, v in options.items() if v is not None})\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Contracts\n\n### MetadataService\n\n```python\nclass MetadataService:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self._metadata_filenames = [\n            \"agent_metadata.yaml\",\n            \"agent.yaml\",\n            \"metadata.yaml\",\n        ]\n\n    def load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata:\n        \"\"\"\n        Load metadata from workspace, falling back through filename list.\n        \n        Raises:\n            FileNotFoundError: If no metadata file exists\n            ValueError: If YAML content violates AgentMetadata schema\n        \"\"\"\n\n    def save_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        \"\"\"\n        Save metadata to {workspace}/agent_metadata.yaml using yaml.dump.\n        \n        Settings:\n            - default_flow_style=False\n            - indent=2\n            - sort_keys=False\n            - model_dump(exclude_none=True)\n        \"\"\"\n\n    def update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata:\n        \"\"\"\n        Load, apply updates, save, and return new AgentMetadata.\n        \"\"\"\n\n    def validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"\n        Validate workspace structure and language-specific requirements.\n        \n        Returns:\n            True if valid\n            \n        Raises:\n            ValueError: If workspace invalid\n        \"\"\"\n\n    def _validate_python_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        \"\"\"\n        Check for at least one *.py file in workspace root.\n        \n        Raises:\n            ValueError(\"No Python files found in workspace\")\n        \"\"\"\n\n    def _validate_java_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None:\n        \"\"\"\n        Check for pom.xml in workspace.\n        \n        Raises:\n            ValueError(\"No pom.xml found in workspace\")\n        \"\"\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### Metadata File Format\n\n```yaml\nagent_name: my-agent\ndescription: A sample agent\nlanguage: python\nentrypoint: python main.py\nport: 8080\nbuild_mode: local\nversion: v1.0.0\nrequirements_file: requirements.txt\nregistry_url: \"\"\nregistry_username: \"\"\nregistry_password: \"\"\nagent_endpoint: null\nworkload_manager_url: null\nrouter_url: null\nreadiness_probe_path: null\nreadiness_probe_port: null\nagent_id: null\nsession_id: null\nimage:\n  name: my-agent\n  tag: latest\n  id: sha256:...\n  size: 150MB\n  build_time: 45s\nauth:\n  type: bearer\nk8s_deployment:\n  type: AgentRuntime\n  namespace: default\n  deployment_name: my-agent\n  service_name: my-agent-service\n  node_port: 30001\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling\n\n### Exception Types\n\n| Exception | Scenario |\n|-----------|----------|\n| `FileNotFoundError` | Workspace or metadata file not found |\n| `ValueError` | Schema validation failure, missing required field |\n| `pydantic.ValidationError` | Pydantic field validation failure |\n\n### Error Handling Patterns\n\n```python\ndef load_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path) -> AgentMetadata:\n    for filename in self._metadata_filenames:\n        path = workspace_path / filename\n        if path.exists():\n            try:\n                with open(path, 'r') as f:\n                    data = yaml.safe_load(f)\n                return AgentMetadata(**data)\n            except yaml.YAMLError as e:\n                raise ValueError(f\"Invalid YAML in {filename}: {e}\")\n            except ValidationError as e:\n                raise ValueError(f\"Schema validation failed: {e}\")\n    \n    raise FileNotFoundError(\n        f\"No metadata file found in {workspace_path}. \"\n        f\"Expected one of: {', '.join(self._metadata_filenames)}\"\n    )\n```\n\n---\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Case | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `test_load_metadata_primary` | Load from `agent_metadata.yaml` |\n| `test_load_metadata_fallback_agent_yaml` | Fallback to `agent.yaml` |\n| `test_load_metadata_fallback_metadata_yaml` | Fallback to `metadata.yaml` |\n| `test_load_metadata_not_found` | Raise `FileNotFoundError` when all missing |\n| `test_load_metadata_invalid_yaml` | Raise `ValueError` on malformed YAML |\n| `test_load_metadata_schema_validation` | Raise `ValueError` on Pydantic validation failure |\n| `test_save_metadata_excludes_none` | Verify `exclude_none=True` behavior |\n| `test_save_metadata_yaml_format` | Verify YAML formatting (indent, no flow style) |\n| `test_update_metadata_partial` | Update specific fields only |\n| `test_validate_python_workspace` | Check for `*.py` files |\n| `test_validate_java_workspace` | Check for `pom.xml` |\n| `test_validate_language_python` | Validate `language='python'` |\n| `test_validate_language_java` | Validate `language='java'` |\n| `test_validate_language_invalid` | Reject invalid language |\n| `test_validate_build_mode_local` | Validate `build_mode='local'` |\n| `test_validate_build_mode_cloud` | Validate `build_mode='cloud'` |\n| `test_validate_port_range` | Validate port 1-65535 |\n| `test_validate_port_out_of_range` | Reject port outside range |\n| `test_metadata_options_from_options` | Create MetadataOptions from dict |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test Case | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `test_pack_loads_metadata` | PackRuntime uses MetadataService.load_metadata |\n| `test_pack_saves_metadata` | PackRuntime uses MetadataService.save_metadata |\n| `test_build_updates_version` | BuildRuntime increments version in metadata |\n| `test_publish_updates_deployment_info` | PublishRuntime updates `k8s_deployment` |\n| `test_invoke_reads_endpoint` | InvokeRuntime reads `agent_endpoint` from metadata |\n| `test_status_reads_metadata` | StatusRuntime loads metadata for status check |\n\n---\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\nтФЬтФАтФА agentcube/\nтФВ   тФЬтФАтФА models/\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py              # Module marker\nтФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА pack_models.py           # MetadataOptions dataclass\nтФВ   тФЬтФАтФА services/\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py              # Services package docstring\nтФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА metadata_service.py      # AgentMetadata, MetadataService\nтФВ   тФЬтФАтФА runtime/\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА pack_runtime.py          # Uses MetadataService\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА build_runtime.py         # Uses MetadataService\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА publish_runtime.py       # Uses MetadataService\nтФВ   тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА invoke_runtime.py        # Uses MetadataService\nтФВ   тФВ   тФФтФАтФА status_runtime.py        # Uses MetadataService\nтФВ   тФФтФАтФА ...\nтФФтФАтФА tests/\n    тФЬтФАтФА test_metadata_service.py     # MetadataService unit tests\n    тФЬтФАтФА test_agent_metadata.py       # AgentMetadata model tests\n    тФЬтФАтФА test_pack_models.py          # MetadataOptions tests\n    тФФтФАтФА integration/\n        тФФтФАтФА test_metadata_flow.py    # Integration tests\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `pydantic` | >=2.0.0 | BaseModel, validators, serialization |\n| `pyyaml` | >=6.0 | YAML load/dump |\n| `pathlib` | stdlib | Path handling |\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n### Constants\n\n```python\nMETADATA_FILENAMES = [\"agent_metadata.yaml\", \"agent.yaml\", \"metadata.yaml\"]\nCANONICAL_METADATA_FILENAME = \"agent_metadata.yaml\"\nSUPPORTED_LANGUAGES = [\"python\", \"java\"]\nSUPPORTED_BUILD_MODES = [\"local\", \"cloud\"]\nDEFAULT_PORT = 8080\n```\n\n### YAML Serialization\n\n```python\nyaml.dump(\n    metadata.model_dump(exclude_none=True),\n    default_flow_style=False,\n    indent=2,\n    sort_keys=False,\n)\n```\n\n### Language Validation\n\nLowercase normalization before validation:\n```python\nlanguage = options.get('language', 'python').lower()\n```\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- cli-toolkit/design.md тАФ CLI toolkit architecture\n- cli-toolkit/spec.md тАФ CLI specification (workspace validation, metadata format)"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-025/design.md","time":{"start":1775876981322,"end":1775876981357}}}}
